{
  "stem": "2718.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Same old story like-- like we have it now and like it was a hundred years ago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's nothing different about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only difference was that maybe 100 years ago, there are were isolated pogroms in Russia or anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and there no mass-- there were no mass murders like it was, for example, in 1944, '45 in Budapest when they lined up people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They dragged them out of the so-called protected houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They dragged them out and shoved them into the venue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These were the very people-- these were the party people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "These were the same people who-- who interrogated in the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "These were the people who-- who put us on the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And these were the people who-- who were most upset when they saw Jews coming back after the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't disappear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't disappear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They-- they were still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The difference was that they turned Communist instead of Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I, like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like any-- any young person in those days, my future was more like planned by my family, by my parents, than by myself.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not that I had any objections to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was going to go to the university and become a-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] get a degree in-- in-- what do you call it-- in general-- general machinery.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What sort of degree is that one?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "An engineer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not an engineer like we call-- everybody calls things an engineer today, but there was such a faculty as an engineer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because-- because they wanted to-- they-- they needed somebody, the family needed somebody, to-- to take over the factory from my grandfather, from my uncle, because I was the next generation.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
